# Netlify rewrites for freepressrelease.io
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Published press releases are RENDERED by the portal app
# (my.freepressrelease.io) but SERVED under this apex. Status 200 = a rewrite
# (proxy): Netlify fetches the target and serves it while the browser URL stays
# freepressrelease.io/press/<slug>. (A 301/302 would change the visible URL —
# don't use those here.) First match wins, so list /press before any catch-all.

/press                https://my.freepressrelease.io/press             200
/press/*              https://my.freepressrelease.io/press/:splat       200

# DB-backed sitemap + RSS for the release pages.
/press-sitemap.xml    https://my.freepressrelease.io/sitemap.xml        200
/press-rss.xml        https://my.freepressrelease.io/rss                200
